\ul  1. INTRODUCTION\par
\ulnone  1.1 Purpose\par
The purpose of creating the seat allocation system is to provide a solution for allocating seats to newly hired employees and reallocating the seats already in use. The number of people working in the organisation is increasing every year. As a result, the organisation will have to accommodate all its employees at its workplace. In this situation, the seat allocation system will help in the allocation of seats  and hence reduce the time and effort of the operational team. \par
1.2 Intended Audience\par
The intended audience of the seat allocation      system would be the operational team and the employees.\par
1.3 Scope\par
The Seat Allocation System is a web application that assists employees and operational team in handling modern-day seating issues at work. Moreover, it is an essential resource in planning that facilitates employees's sitting within the bounds of the workplace.\par
